caption:
F E S T I V E • T E A 🎄🍰☕️
All I want for Christmas is...food! 
It’s that time of year when we visit the @shangrilasydney for @annapolyviou’s ‘Festive Afternoon Tea’. Three tiers of sweets, savouries and my fav...scones! 
Don’t forget to check out the real #gingerbread life-sized train in the hotel lobby until 31 Dec. 😍 #SydXmas

D O N U T S 🍩😍
As someone who’s addicted to @tinykitchentm videos, these mini donut earrings are next level! @sparkleliscious 
Who else loves mini food?

S’ M O R E S 🍫🍦🔥
Late night treats @thegrovela. We know people flock to @dominiqueansel for the cronuts but we love the ‘Frozen S’more’: honey marshmallow, vanilla ice cream, chocolate wafer crisps and it is torched tableside! #discoverla #visitcalifornia 📍Los Angeles, CA

B U R G E R 🍔🍟
Sometimes you just need a double double from @innout #foodcrewtravel #visitcalifornia 📍@visitWeHo, California

B E V • H I L L S • H O T E L 
Cocktails at breakfast, why not! 
At the iconic @bevhillshotel Cabana Club. 🍹🌴
#discoverLA #DCmoments #foodcrewtravel 📍LA, California

P A S T R I E S 💗✌🏼
Croissants, cruffins, danishes...oh my! @mrholmesbakehouse #foodcrewtravel #alwaysSF 📍San Francisco, California

W I N E R Y 🥂🐴
Soaking up the afternoon sun at @tamberbey winery and meeting the resident horses of Sundance Ranch. #visitnapavalley 📍Calistoga, @visitnapavalley

C H O W D E R 🦀🍞
When it’s absolutely normal in @onlyinSF to eat your meal out of a @boudinbakery sourdough bread bowl. 
#visitcalifornia #foodcrewtravel #alwayssf 📍San Francisco, California

Day One of our Cali vacay!
Siteseeing but first @sightglass 🇺🇸 @visitcalifornia @onlyinSF #foodcrewtravel #alwayssf

H O T C A K E S 🥞
Serious cravings right now for @Billsaustralia famous ricotta #hotcakes 
Who’s had these and know what we’re talking about.👌🏻🤤 #sydneyeats
